label: SENT
text:
One of the things that I have definitely learned in this
 experience, and I don't think I would have known, or it wouldn't have
 shaped me as it has, is migrating here and having to adapt to the culture
 and to the country itself, has shown me or opened my eyes a lot in terms
 of, you know, everyone, as an individual is just who they decide to be.
name: Ana
